response.overview: On November 28, 2017, Nagano Athletic Park Gymnasium in Nagano hosted Day 9 of NJPW World Tag League 2017.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, Hiromu Takahashi & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Gedo, Kazuchika Okada & Will Ospreay).  The card also featured Juice Robinson & Sami Callihan vs Manabu Nakanishi & Yuji Nagata.  Other wrestlers on the show include Davey Boy Smith Jr., El Desperado and Lance Archer, and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 9
